.TH JUMPER "1" "November 2024" "jumper v0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
jumper \- Secure Ncurses-like SSH Jump Server
.SH DESCRIPTION
jumper provides a secure SSH jump server frontend for Linux systems. Jumper features an intuitive, ncurses-inspired interface that makes setup and management straightforward. It automates environment creation, jump target management, and key imports in a clean, user-friendly terminal interface.
.SS "Usage:"
.IP
jumper [command] [options]
.PP
Commands:
.TP
run
Run jumper normally.
.TP
\fB\-\-restrict\-admin\fR
Prevents access to admin menu even with password. (Default: false)
.TP
passwd <username>
Change jumper admin password for an already setup jumper chroot user.
.TP
deluser <username>
Delete a jumper chroot user along with the users configuration and jumper SSH key.
.TP
\fB\-\-confirm, \-y\fR
Confirms deletion of jumper chroot user. (Default: false)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-help\fR
Display help screen.
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
Display version information.
